Important note on subject matter:

The profiles in this repository are based on publicly available materials about
real individuals. The "thinking model" distillations are post-hoc inferences by
the author and do not represent endorsements or statements by the subjects
themselves. Each profile contains explicit caveats distinguishing direct quotes
from inferred patterns. If you are a subject of a profile and wish to request
correction or removal, please open an issue.
